name: "Mezzanine Resident"
description:
“Mezzanine Resident” is part 2 of a 3-part story that portrays someone trapped by fear inside his little dreams. He is merely living because he is so afraid of seeing what will happen to the others that he cannot step outside. Always that same scene in front of his window: the airborne saliva of the upstairs neighbor. 
Why did this man lose his hair?
Is it because he lost hope strand by strand?
Or is it the testosterone?
First one to reach his baldhead with his piss gets dibs on asking!
